lines.text: You could be loved by me!
I could be loved by you.
You COULD be loved by me!
I could be HURT by you!
I didn't even read the questions, I just took a number 2 pencil and filled in the bubbles as fast as I could!
What did you put for sex?
Work, work, work! That's all you do! Chris, you need to have some fun!
Fun! You know, starts with an F, ends in an N, has a U in the middle!
Oh, yeah I've heard of it.
I can't help the way I am. I don't know why I do the things I do. You just have to trust me on that!
